# UI vocabulary

When the user refers to UI by informal names, map them using `docs/UI_VOCABULARY.md`.

## Listing workflow MessageBarInput

| Reference ID | Meaning |
|--------------|---------|
| `listing-bar-pre-link` | MessageBarInput in CreateWorkflow **before** a link is submitted — hero layout, “Reimagine Any Listing”, `listingLinkSubmitted === false` |
| `listing-bar-post-link` | Same MessageBarInput **after** submit — fixed **bottom** float (transparent wrapper, pill only), always visible (no auto-hide), with integrated chat-context selector inside the pill, `listingLinkSubmitted === true` |

Aliases: “message bar before/after link”, “hero bar”, “bottom bar / dock” → same IDs.

Code: `CreateWorkflow.jsx` (wrapper + `listingLinkSubmitted`), `MessageBarInput.jsx`, `ChatContextSelector.jsx`, `constants/chatContextModes.js`, `App.jsx` (`listingLinkSubmitted` / `testListingLinkSubmitted`).

Do not treat these as two different components — one `MessageBarInput`, two layout states.

## Listing workflow source listing summary

| Reference ID | Meaning |
|-----|---|
| `listing-source-summary` | Compact panel rendered by `ListingDetails` above `PhotoGallery` after link submit (`listingLinkSubmitted === true` and `listing` is loaded). Shows fetched eBay listing: title, `{sku} · date · N images · Cat …` meta line, price right-aligned, scrollable description. Replaces the old “Current SKU” banner and the bottom `ListingDetails` panel. |

Aliases: “source listing card”, “listing summary”, “top listing details” → `listing-source-summary`.

Code: `ListingDetails.jsx`, `CreateWorkflow.jsx` (placement + `listing`/`photos`/`sku` props), `utils/listingDisplay.js` (shared formatters with `GeneratedListingCard.jsx`).
